    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_02-suz041.m4a",
      "text": "それなら撮影中に私が怒って大御所と喧嘩する方が\n番組が盛り上がっていいかもしれませんわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then if I got angry during the shoot and fought the photographer‚\nit’ll be more dramatic for the program.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 339.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "すず？　さっきから何をぶつぶつ言ってるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu? What have you been muttering about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 342.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_02-suz042.m4a",
      "text": "みなまで言わなくとも分かってますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand‚ even if you don’t tell me everything!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 346.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_02-suz043.m4a",
      "text": "安心なさい。この仕事、トップアイドル成宮すずが\n完璧にこなしてご覧にいれますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t worry. Just watch top idol Suzu Narumiya\ndo this job perfectly!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 354.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうか。それとカメラマンは気難しい人だから\n何を言われても怒ったりせず言われた通りにするんだぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I see. Also‚ the photographer is rather fussy‚\nso whatever he says‚ just go along with it and don’t get upset.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 362.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_02-suz044.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり！！　完璧に理解しましたわ！！\n撮影では撮れ高たっぷりに盛り上げて差し上げますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I knew it! I understand perfectly!\nI’ll make the shoot go really well‚ with plenty of usable footage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 370.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_02-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "……なぁ、やっぱり少し休んだ方がいいんじゃないか？\n疲れていると判断力が鈍るって言うし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Perhaps it really might be better if you rested a bit.\nIf you’re too tired‚ it can affect your judgment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 379.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_02-suz045.m4a",
      "text": "問題ありませんわ！\n大船に乗ったつもりで私に任せなさい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s no problem!\nJust leave it to me‚ it’ll be smooth sailing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 385.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_02-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "（凄い自信だな……ここはすずを信じて任せてみるか）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Such confidence… Can I really trust Suzu enough to leave it all to her?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 389.6333333333,
